<l>orunā ḷeḻunāḷpōṟ celluñcēṭ ceṉṟār </l>
<l> varunāḷvait tēṅku pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who suffer waiting for the day of return of their distant lovers one day is as long as seven days.</l>
